TRXC How many times have you seen a post re the value of Transenterix patents intellectual property Well whatever those are and I doubt they are much they are mortgaged The May 23 2018 refinancing with Hercules provides that the intellectual property of Transenterix is security for the loan That loan by the way was a refinancing of prior debt and the initial 20 million tranche was used immediately for that purpose The remaining 20 million is available only if Transenterix meets sales and profitability goals which is unlikely meaning that the Hercules loan is exhaustedirtransenterixcomnode11
